column14: 1. Start your questions and answers in the 2nd row.
2. Column A should contain category titles.
3. Column B is for the questions. Column C is for the answers.
4. Columns D E and F are for Choice options for multiple-choice games.
5. Column G is for answer hint for interactive choice games.
6. Column H I J K L and M is for bonus questions and answers for quiz bowl games.
7. Columns D E F G H I J K L and M are optional.
8. Use the exact words "Final Factile" as the category name for Final Factile
9. You can also write "Final Factile : Category Title" to specify category name for Final Factile question
